In a large bowl, combine the vegetable juice, lime juice, 1/2 teaspoon (2 ml) hot-pepper sauce, garlic, sugar, cumin, and salt. Whisk to mix. Add the pasta, ham, beans, corn, Cheddar, tomatoes, scallions, and olives. Toss to mix. Taste and add up to 1/2 teaspoon (2 ml) more hot-pepper sauce, if desired.